</div>
</div>
</div>

<div class="mt-2 p-5 rounded-lg border border-accent-gold/20 bg-[#FAF9F6] dark:bg-primary/20 flex items-start gap-4 transition-all hover:border-accent-gold/40">
<div class="flex items-center h-6">
<input class="size-5 rounded border-gray-300 text-primary focus:ring-accent-gold/50 cursor-pointer" id="prerequisite" type="checkbox"/>
</div>
<label class="text-sm text-primary dark:text-gray-200 cursor-pointer leading-relaxed" for="prerequisite">
<span class="font-bold">Requisito Obrigatório:</span> Declaro que completei com êxito o <span class="italic text-accent-gold font-medium">Modern Facial Surgery - Advanced Training Program</span> e possuo o certificado de conclusão.
                    </label>
</div>

<div class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-primary text-white p-8 group">

<div class="absolute top-0 right-0 -mt-10 -mr-10 size-64 bg-accent-gold/10 rounded-full blur-3xl group-hover:bg-accent-gold/20 transition-all duration-700"></div>
<div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-6 items-start">
<div class="size-12 rounded-full bg-white/10 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 border border-white/10">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-accent-gold">info</span>
</div>
<div class="flex-1">
<h3 class="text-accent-gold text-lg font-serif font-medium mb-2">Próximos Passos</h3>
<p class="text-gray-300 text-sm leading-relaxed font-light">
                                Após o envio desta inscrição, nossa equipe de credenciamento entrará em contato via WhatsApp em até 48 horas úteis. Você receberá as instruções para o envio da documentação de <strong>5 casos clínicos</strong> para avaliação pessoal do Dr. Robério Brandão.
                            </p>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<div class="pt-4 flex justify-center w-full">
<button class="group relative w-full sm:w-auto min-w-[320px] overflow-hidden rounded-lg bg-primary px-8 py-5 text-center transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-accent-gold/10 border border-accent-gold" type="button">
<span class="relative z-10 flex items-center justify-center gap-2 text-sm font-bold tracking-[0.1em] uppercase text-accent-gold transition-colors group-hover:text-white">
                            Enviar Inscrição para Certificação
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:translate-x-1">arrow_forward</span>
</span>

<div class="absolute inset-0 z-0 bg-accent-gold opacity-0 transition-opacity duration-300 group-hover:opacity-10"></div>
</button>
</div>
</form>
</div>

<footer class="mt-12 text-center pb-8">
<div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-6 text-sm font-medium text-gray-400 mb-4">
